**Overview**

This dashboards is used to monitor and troubleshoot ingest performance from integrations.  

**For the best experience, filter on the specific Agent of interest to visualize the metrics correctly.  
Use the Metric counters to Drilldown to the specific Input Dashboard.**  

**This dashboard requires that "Collect Agent Metrics" are configured on the relevant Elastic Agent policy.**
